reviews.reviewText: Very practical coiled charging cable that reduces space in the car and leaves no stray wires. Elastic enough to stretch and then return to its original size. It works great so it's neat when connected and neat when disconnected. It never tangles and reduces damage.

reviews.reviewText: I use this in place of my iPhone bedside charging cable, and it's a sturdy braided cable that stretches well and still has good stretch so you don't end up with a stretched cable. Works well with my fast charger and the cable end looks very sturdy.
